PRIVILEGE IBIZA VIP TABLE AND ENTRY

Still deemed the largest nightclub in the world, Privilege is one place you probably will not mind getting lost in.

Ushuaia Ibiza Vip Table and Vip Entry

The roof stands twenty-five metres high, and the main room can house more people than you could fathom.

PRIVILEGE VIP TABLES IBIZA

Please use the following information as a guide, prices may vary from party to party.

GOLD AREA begins at 200€per person and this includes VIP entry, a table in the VIP area and drinks to the value of 200€pp

BLACK AREA begins at 200/250€per person and this includes VIP entry, a table in the VIP area and drinks to the value of 200/250€pp

SILVER AREA begins at 200/250€per person and this includes VIP entry, a table in the VIP area and drinks to the value of 200/250€pp

PLATINUM AREA begins at 400/50€per person and this includes VIP entry, a table in the VIP area and drinks to the value of 400/500€pp

WHITE AREA begins at 400/50€per person and this includes VIP entry, a table in the VIP area and drinks to the value of 400/500€pp

WHITE AREA exclusive for 10.000 euros for upto 25 guests

Please contact for our concierge deals by completeing the enquiry form or contact us via call / text / WhatsApp on +34616318262.

WHY RESERVE YOUR PRIVILEGE IBIZA VIP TABLE WITH US?

VIP is still something which Privilege does best. Their esteemed history in lavish nights allows you to experience something special. With a range of VIP packages available for both the main room and the Vista Club, they will ensure that everyone there will wonder who you are.

By booking the best tables within your budget, handling payments, and sending confirmations on your behalf, we ensure you have the highest VIP experience possible. We also offer full concierge services for VIP tables, restaurant reservations, transport requests, and boat charters.

Host entry and assistance

Your allocated host will arrive at the club before you to check your table. Furthermore, they will arrange your drinks when getting to the club and fast-track your entry with no queue. They will take care of payments to ensure there are no issues. All this will ensure you have everything you need to enjoy your night.

We can also assist with transport to/from the club if required – click here for details about our Ibiza Transportation Services.
